{"tid":2246334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民大會打對台 拜登收視率勝侵","createTime":"2020-10-17T03:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T18:08:58.000Z","uid":231908,"like":4,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"af73d76b79552a86edb319f5c2267d9e8e3df4f3","tid":2246334,"uid":231908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T03:29:14.000Z","msg":"根據尼爾森公司（Nielsen）今天公布的數字，美國前副總統拜登參與市民大會的電視收視率，高過總統川普在同時段的類似活動，兩人幾週後將在11月3日總統大選對決。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，拜登（Joe Biden）昨晚在迪士尼旗下美國廣播公司（ABC）播出的市民大會（Town hall）討論90分鐘期間，平均有1510萬人收看。康卡斯特公司（Comcast）旗下國家廣播公司（NBC）、微軟國家廣播公司（MSNBC）及CNBC有線頻道轉播川普的市民大會，吸引1350萬名觀眾。<br />\n<br />\n而在川普和拜登同時打對台的一小時中，拜登平均有1430萬收視人口，高於川普的1350萬人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nbcnews.com/news/all/biden-beats-trump-town-hall-ratings-showdown-n1243785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fall%2Fbiden-beats-trump-town-hall-ratings-showdown-n1243785&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24haozMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=e36e6d73\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nbcnews.com/news/all/biden-beats-trump-town-hall-ratings-showdown-n1243785</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.tenor.com/images/c7a2c0ab08c8b234d152b22a2a33ee72/tenor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tenor.com%2Fimages%2Fc7a2c0ab08c8b234d152b22a2a33ee72%2Ftenor.gif&h=e97f7e45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">點解既點解既，連兒口中既沈默大多數係咪連電視都無</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7183bbaf43a38e4295892607defb39a312fc2b","tid":2246334,"uid":48083,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"因為個個都等biden回應佢個仔單野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a650bf8bdd09d8bf9dc39af3286b7b60ca4386","tid":2246334,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"